  "keyFeatures": [
    "7 domain-adaptive ECG augmentations (frequency warping, medical mixup, bandpass filtering, CutMix, motion artifacts, per-channel noise, temporal dropout)",
    "SimCLR contrastive pretraining achieving 0.8717 AUROC with only 10% labeled data",
    "BYOL momentum-based pretraining as an alternative framework",
    "Label-efficient fine-tuning via linear probing on frozen SSL encoders",
    "Multi-seed validation (10 seeds) with confidence intervals for statistical robustness",
    "Supervised CNN baseline with Focal Loss and oversampling for class imbalance",
    "Traditional ML baseline (Random Forest, XGBoost) with handcrafted ECG features",
    "Transfer evaluation on MIT-BIH arrhythmia dataset",
    "Per-class performance analysis for 5 cardiovascular disease classes (NORM, MI, STTC, HYP, CD)",
    "Publication-ready figure and table generation"
  ],
